{"TopicId":185245,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"How do I get badges.","CreatedByName":"DRAG0Nmon","CreatedById":196609,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-07T22:06:06Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"DRAG0Nmon","CreatedById":196609,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-07T22:06:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have completed a few challenges, and there were badges available for them. But how to I claim the badges, so they show up whenever I post?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Gargamel","CreatedById":64714,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-07T23:18:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit your profile so that the badges you want to display are shown.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMoved to Kerbal Network.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vanamonde","CreatedById":27914,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-08T01:32:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCopy the badge from the challenge creator\u0027s post.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Lapis","CreatedById":193784,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-08T13:17:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRight click on the badge and press \u0022copy image location\u0022 then go to your signature and paste it in there. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-06-08T13:18:21Z\u0022 title=\u002206/08/2019 01:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJune 8, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by lapis\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"4x4cheesecake","CreatedById":187982,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-08T13:41:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223614275\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022185245\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221559957521\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002227914\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vanamonde\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, Vanamonde said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCopy the badge from the challenge creator\u0027s post.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut you should be sure, that you are actually allowed to do this \u003Cimg alt=\u0022;)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUsually, submitting an entry doesn\u0027t mean, you\u0027re instantly allowed to grab the badge, you have to wait for the maintainer of the challenge to review the entry so the he/she can decide, if your entry is conform with the rules of the challenge. When in doubt, kindly ask in the challenge\u00A0 if you are allowed to grab the badge \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DRAG0Nmon","CreatedById":196609,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-06-08T16:34:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, it worked!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}